{
  "stem": "4247.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because my-- in my mind, I thought, well next time we go to [NON-ENGLISH], we don't have to go by passport.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And those-- those ugly Czechs, you know, whom as a child of eight, I would have killed with a sword, right?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Will not to rule that part of historical Hungary.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What I thought of that, well, it was very interesting.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a very interesting-- interesting mixture, as I said to you earlier.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I started to-- I started to query things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and it took me a year, a couple of years, indeed, to realize that this is nothing but ugly propaganda, right?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm not as ugly as they paint me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- but during those two years, I remember I was anxious to recite those poems even better.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was anxious to kick another goal for our team, just to prove that, you know, I can do better than you can, right?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and as I said, it was a-- it was a-- a transitional time of two years before I realized that I'm right and you are wrong.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- I was 13, 14, 15.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's-- that's-- that was the time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From my parents?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Look, my parents, my father was essentially a conventional, [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] meek, law-abiding citizen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His-- his behavior, and therefore his example to me-- to me was that, look, this is the law.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We have to abide the law, right?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was the very interesting part of the whole anti-Jewish campaign, which was getting uglier and uglier.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Even the last, most ugly scene, when-- when [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the crease appeared on the wall that you have to go to the gas chamber, right?",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
